# forge write whitelist (template)
#
# Setup: bash $FRAMEWORK_DIR/scripts/setup-cc.sh — substitutes ${FRAMEWORK_DIR}
# and ${HOME} with detected absolute paths, writes the result to
# .claude/path-whitelist.txt (gitignored).
#
# The hook orchestrators/claude-code/hooks/path-whitelist-guard.sh blocks
# Edit/Write/NotebookEdit on paths that don't match any pattern below.
# Glob: ** matches across directories, * matches one segment.

# Framework repo itself
${FRAMEWORK_DIR}/**

# All consumer projects under PROJECTS_DIR
${HOME}/projects/**

# User-level CC config (settings.json, agents/skills symlinks)
${HOME}/.claude/settings.json
